column5: This is a nice, secluded property in the Clarksville neighborhood. There is a queen size bed as well as a pull-out sleeper sofa. The unit is quiet and clean, has 1 bed and a pull-out sofa with amenities including fully stocked kitchen, cable TV/WiFi, and one free on-site parking spot. (Additional parking available in surrounding neighborhood but requires walking.)
column8: Relaxing Clarksville Apt - 5 min from downtown.
